{"tid":1633513,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"[緊急] 今日唔出等聽日全民照常返工先出嚟？","createTime":"2019-10-07T04:18:49.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-07T04:40:01.000Z","uid":16981,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"a71f43e5272eec92fd3179f3b00086f64a132c6b","tid":1633513,"uid":16981,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T04:18:50.000Z","msg":"休乜嘢息？得閒先開下花、裝下修、私下了？<br />\n今日重陽啊！最起碼都出嚟紀念下班義士啦！<br />\n<br />\n今日黨鐵又停開全力搶修<br />\n又想聽日一切回復正常？ <br />\n<br />\n放假就閂晒商場封晒站咁比你哋慢慢玩，你哋唔十八區遍地開花仲攪一區大遊行，而對家就set好rb、集中警力大圍捕、查你巴士、專捉細路靚女<br />\n<br />\n平日又照常打工嘅繼續打工，開鋪嘅繼續開鋪，咁點樣可以影響到成個社會嘅運作，而對大部分人嘅工作日唔大影響，又點樣施到壓比政府？<br />\n<br />\n搶修都要佢星期一至五先嚟攪啦下話？<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">日間紀念義士<br />\n夜晚遍地開花</span></span><br />\n</span></span>"},{"pid":"8e47e19109c85afb5718e67a09a4033aa45601e5","tid":1633513,"uid":16981,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T04:21:47.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b4ab072596f99c0fe49a842b807f632f68b57203","tid":1633513,"uid":16981,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T04:21:58.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"cad0a19f0b20a309e2f22fe1e8f2bb221b074f0b","tid":1633513,"uid":16981,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T04:22:12.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d9a036ef41853b12c3243384b8c7bb00d35fa6ee","tid":1633513,"uid":16981,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T04:22:25.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"513667247f0c867fb3552e8abe50c8d6faa4b507","tid":1633513,"uid":16981,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T04:22:35.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"432bcb72df8b2948b2114f400b73c9aecb27c258","tid":1633513,"uid":218298,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T04:24:45.000Z","msg":"「緊急」要草船借箭啊！！！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1629930\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1629930</a><br />\n